data.description: Welcome to a Bright & Sunny top floor move-in ready condo, 2 Beds 2 Baths unit with a gas fireplace and a private balcony. Open living room and dining area. Spacious bedrooms with a large custom closet area, and in-unit laundry room. Kitchen features LG & GE stainless steel appliances with recently replaced fridge, dishwasher, microwave with granite counter tops. Top floor, high ceilings and plenty of natural light. Incredible location minutes from Fairfax Corner, Fair Oaks Mall, Wegmans, Costco, Downtown Fairfax City and major commuter routes including Route 50 and I-66. ** Assumable VA Loan option is available as well ** Contact us for more details** Assumable VA Loan option is available - Interest rate 2.99% **
